<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/cheerio" rel="nofollow">Cheerio</a> is a DOM parser that I enjoy using. I haven't tried this, but <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-dom-massager" rel="nofollow">grunt-dom-massager</a> allows you to load Cheerio in your Gruntfile.</p>
    </div>
